Description:
    Generates components for our view layer

Example:
    rails generate component Thing

    This will create:
        app/frontend/thing/thing.js
        app/frontend/thing/thing.css
        app/frontend/thing/index.html.erb
        app/frontend/thing/show.html.erb
        app/frontend/thing/edit.html.erb
        app/frontend/thing/new.html.erb
